  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the wholemeal flour and cook, stirring constantly, for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the corn kernels and cook for 3-4 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the saffron threads, ground cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Pour in the chicken broth and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 15-20 minutes or until the liquid has been absorbed and the corn is tender.",
    "Stir in the grated cheddar cheese until melted.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley and a dollop of coconut milk if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
